```{.python .input  n=2}
from iopro import PostgresAdapter
import geopandas as gpd
from shapely.geometry import Polygon, MultiPolygon
```

```{.python .input  n=3}
def arrays_to_geoseries(arrays):
    return gpd.GeoSeries([MultiPolygon([Polygon(node_j[0]) for node_j in node['geom']]) for node in arrays])
```

```{.python .input  n=5}
adapter = PostgresAdapter('host=127.0.0.1 port=5432 dbname=gisdb user=docker password=docker', table='tl_2014_tract')
```

```{.python .input  n=6}
%%time
fast_arrays = adapter[:]
```
